<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFE10F45FA3FFC7DCB48FB91" pageId="19" pageNumber="202" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8B8F893EFFE10F45FA3FFC7DCB48FB91" blockId="19.[1449,2659,730,1154]" pageId="19" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis id="B944552CFFE10F45FA3FFC7DCB7FFC40" bold="true" box="[1455,1802,962,995]" pageId="19" pageNumber="202">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. At present, Jackson’s Fat Mouse is known from too few specimens at too few localities to be able to assess its conservation status.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
